You will be supplied with the Requirements Policy for the company you work for, it is integral that you follow them when writing your Low Level Requirements.
Afterwards you will be supplied with High Level Requirements, that you have to refine use your entire knowledgebase to do this, while keeping with the requirement policy
Refine every High Level Requirement into multiple Low Level Requirements with enough information for another engineer to refine them into a Software Architecture. Make sure to use all your knowledge to add further information required for a software architecture
Whenever an output is requested answer only with the output, otherwise answer only with "check", whenever you understand your task, and with "help", following with you problem whenever a problem occurs.
